    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >There's a person inside the vending machine!</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[The background and story of the game]</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225850/extras/e97b2c88c2636ed67dad060ab09cb8a1.poster.avif?t=1755140846\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225850/extras/e97b2c88c2636ed67dad060ab09cb8a1.webm?t=1755140846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225850/extras/e97b2c88c2636ed67dad060ab09cb8a1.mp4?t=1755140846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Urban fantasy game set in a city where strange beings live in hiding.<br>Examine the bizarre city with Nabi, the protagonist tasked with monitoring and managing strange beings.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225850/extras/5dfb149617a4b56e59177f91d0f7271d.poster.avif?t=1755140846\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225850/extras/5dfb149617a4b56e59177f91d0f7271d.webm?t=1755140846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225850/extras/5dfb149617a4b56e59177f91d0f7271d.mp4?t=1755140846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Vending machines that exist everywhere in the city, and no one cares.<br>Nabi lives in a vending machine in the city and is an investigator for MonsterA, which keeps out strange beings from the public. What other incidents should we investigate and resolve today?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What kind of drink would you like?</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Drink a variety of drinks and use your fun skills]</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225850/extras/2334905626fcb25aa918c0f06854ff95.poster.avif?t=1755140846\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225850/extras/2334905626fcb25aa918c0f06854ff95.webm?t=1755140846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225850/extras/2334905626fcb25aa918c0f06854ff95.mp4?t=1755140846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A Nabi can use its power as a drink. What kind of drinks do you like? Try some fun abilities while drinking your favorite drinks?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Take care of the vending machine]</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225850/extras/aa80a88cf9dc8d874b35ffa62d834bba.poster.avif?t=1755140846\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225850/extras/aa80a88cf9dc8d874b35ffa62d834bba.webm?t=1755140846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225850/extras/aa80a88cf9dc8d874b35ffa62d834bba.mp4?t=1755140846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Research new drinks in vending machines, and launch them. They will be very helpful for researcher activities.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225850/extras/5cc6c929287a1beb67ba7ae5dfcc11d6.poster.avif?t=1755140846\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225850/extras/5cc6c929287a1beb67ba7ae5dfcc11d6.webm?t=1755140846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225850/extras/5cc6c929287a1beb67ba7ae5dfcc11d6.mp4?t=1755140846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Earn activity money by selling drinks with the investigator's supporter Oracle.<br>Various research activities and upgrades always require money.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Oh, by the way! And it's more comfortable than you think…</strong></h2>",
